Detailed Description

An context representation.

Think about a context as being similar to a directory in a file system.

Member Enumeration Documentation

anonymous enum
 

Enumeration values:
MAX_OBJECT_NAME_SIZE  Max sizes of names (Not too sure about this value).
MAX_CONTEXT_NAME_SIZE  Max size of context name.
